<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.5.3">
<l>vīvi liṉpa mikavellai nikaḻntana maccutaṉ</l>
<l>vīvil cīraṉ malarkkaṇṇaṉ viṇṇōr perumāṉṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>vīvil kāla micaimālaika ḷētti mēvappeṟṟēṉ</l>
<l>vīvi liṉpamika vellai nikaḻntaṉaṉ mēviyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our Acyuta who much passes the limites of imperishable pleasure,</l>
<l>him of imperishable excellence, Kṛṣṇa with flower eyes, the great lord of the celestials</l>
<l>praising him as imperishable time with a musical garland I have obtained that he resides [in me].</l>
<l>Being attached [to him] I have passed the limits of imperishable pleasure.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
